        public java.util.List<Receipt> getReceipts()
        Returns receipts, or an empty list if getRequestStatus() is not PurchaseUpdatesResponse.RequestStatus.SUCCESSFUL, or there are no receipts. Canceled entitlement receipt may have null value for all other properties in Receipt object except sku while interacting with previous versions of the Amazon Appstore.
